to do with karma.

104
00:04:40,933 --> 00:04:41,933
The difference is...

105
00:04:41,933 --> 00:04:43,066
- Oh don't start 
explaining to me

106
00:04:43,066 --> 00:04:45,666
about transmigration of souls.

107
